    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is a total gem and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been absolutely pampered and is in truly pristine condition\u2014not a single blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone to take it home. Seriously, you have to see it to believe how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
