    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This investment-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW engineering. At its heart is the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is in superlative condition, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a pristine suspension geometry that preserves the car's legendary handling dynamics. The paint depth and interior materials remain in concours-standard state, free of the typical wear found in higher-mileage examples. A mechanically transparent and structurally unblemished icon for the serious collector.",
